'''Abdulla Abdullaev''' ({{lang-x2|uz|Abdulla Qahramonjon oʻgʻli Abdullayev|Абдулла Қаҳрамонжон ўғли Абдуллаев}}; born 1 September 1997) is an Uzbek professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays for [[Dibba FC|Dibba]] and the [[Uzbekistan national football team|Uzbekistan national team]].

==Career==
===International===
Abdullaev made his debut for the [[Uzbekistan national football team|Uzbekistan]] main team on 5 September 2021 in a [[Friendly (sport)|Friendly]] match against [[Sweden men's national football team|Sweden]].<ref>[https://www.national-football-teams.com/matches/report/31773/Sweden_Uzbekistan.html Sweden 2–1 Uzbekistan]</ref> Named to the Uzbekistan national team squad for the [[2026 FIFA World Cup]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://t.me/uzpfl/77948|title=UzPFL|website=Telegram|access-date=2026-05-29}}</ref>

